<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="chase-v">chase <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tʃeɪs/    美 /tʃeɪs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>追逐；追赶：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Kids are chasing around the house.
孩子们在房子周围相互追逐。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In the dream Peter saw himself chased by a fierce wolf, and he woke suddenly with a start.
彼得梦见被一只恶狼追赶，突然间惊醒了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>驱逐；赶走：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>chase</strong> a dog <strong>out of</strong> a garden
把狗赶出花园</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>追求；努力获得：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>chase after</strong> one’s dream
追求梦想</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Top graduates from universities are chased by major companies.
优秀的大学毕业生受到大公司的青睐。</p><footer>2014 江苏</footer></div></div>